4Geeks Academy offers a Data Science & Machine Learning bootcamp designed for beginners with no prior knowledge. Over 16 weeks, students engage in three classes per week, with a maximum class size of 12. The curriculum includes Python, SQL, and data visualization tools, focusing on creating predictive models and understanding algorithms. Graduates can earn a recognized certificate and have opportunities to develop their own AI projects. The course is available in English and Spanish, catering to diverse learners. For more information, visit [4Geeks Academy](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/datascience-machine-learning). stop